      "五、"
    ],
    "pages": [
      1
    ],
    "page_start": 1,
    "page_end": 1,
    "content": "五、 營運衝擊分析(Business Impact Analysis, BIA)：評估核心業務中斷對\n金融機構所造成衝擊之分析方法。",
    "is_leaf": true,
    "table_count": 0,
    "tables": []
  },
  {
    "file_name": "金融機構資訊作業韌性規範_20240521.md",
    "node_name": "六、",
    "level": 1,
    "sibling_order": 6,
    "path_key": "2.6",
    "path_names": [
